{
  "name": "Manipulate Density",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/blood.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain the following abilities which manipulate the density of the target&#8217;s blood:</p>\n<p>As a (quicken) ability, the target&#8217;s blood becomes lighter. The target gains a circumstance bonus on Acrobatics checks equal to 2 + 1/2 your caster level for the duration of your blood control. If you spend an additional spell point, the target also gains compression as per the universal monster rule for the duration of your blood control.</p>\n<p>As a (still) ability, the target&#8217;s blood becomes dense. The target gains DR/slashing equal to 1/3 your caster level (minimum 1) for the duration of your blood control. If you spend an additional spell point, the target instead gains DR/adamantine equal to 1/2 your caster level (minimum 1) for this duration. Once the DR/adamantine has prevented damage to the target equal to 10 times your caster level, the DR/adamantine ends immediately and the target gains DR/slashing equal to 1/3 your caster level (minimum 1) for the remainder of this effect&#8217;s duration.</p>\n",
